{"tid":946780,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實中港台台關係都幾玄妙下","createTime":"2018-12-18T18:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T10:50:49.000Z","uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a456f62d646b81688932ef23ca43ec3493e5314f","tid":946780,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T18:41:43.000Z","msg":"中港台 話就話一個中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但各自有自己文化 語言 法律 政治 教育 制度 等等 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以次次去中國/台灣 係覺得去左第二個國家咁 而三個地方嘅人又會互相睇唔起對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時佢地發生啲咩事我地係完全無感覺 例如話台灣地震我會覺得 : 關我閪事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n所以我嘅問題係：1.其他大嘅國家 eg 美國咁，唔同洲/城市嘅人會唔會當對方係自己人 因為美國唔同洲嘅文化差異應該比中港台細（？）<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 究竟世上有無國家嘅情況同中港台一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無外國巴打可以解答下小弟問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc999949e76c19a8ba663a3631942a7b7c8ac82","tid":946780,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T18:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8382b6699fdc2abe3061b476c59b183903e5c963","tid":946780,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T18:54:38.000Z","msg":"人地係直接變成一個國家 <br />\n好似係大部份歐洲國家經歷過某樣時期<br />\n但中國直接比人打完後復興 無左中華民國建立三樣野<br />\n個三樣野係最終走向共和 定 分裂多個國家 但可以成立中亞組織 類似歐盟"},{"pid":"5d6495a75b1ad97a31e7fec3767ca1c95f718caa","tid":946780,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bed708fc587794973a93b603841464be03794f8","tid":946780,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"根本係唔同國家<br />\n只係為咗政治理由格硬老屈係同一國"},{"pid":"445cfdb08e0f0034452a554a6ed6633e529992e8","tid":946780,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9254924869bff5cb929303c3bf8d405406b0d592","tid":946780,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7978cd6c9901ddbbe6e63ecb39f7faebc8f20a","tid":946780,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T08:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},